<h3 id="override">Override</h3>

<p>μνΌν΄λμ¤μ—μ„ μ‹¤μ²΄ λ©”μ†λ“λ¥Ό μ¬μ •μν•λ ¤λ©΄ override ν•μ •μλ¥Ό μ¶”κ°€ν•΄μ•Όν•λ‹¤. κ·Έλ¬λ‚ μ¶”μƒ λ©”μ†λ“λ¥Ό κµ¬ν„ν•λ” κ²½μ° override ν•μ •μκ°€ ν•„μ”λ” μ—†λ‹¤. Scala λ” override ν‚¤μ›λ“λ¥Ό μ‚¬μ©ν•΄ λ¶€λ¨ ν΄λμ¤μ λ©”μ†λ“λ¥Ό μ¬μ •μν•©λ‹λ‹¤.</p>

<p>μλ¥Ό ν†µν•΄ μ•μ•„λ³΄κ² μµλ‹λ‹¤.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Example</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-scala highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">abstract</span> <span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">Test</span> <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="k">var</span> <span class="n">message</span> <span class="k">:</span> <span class="kt">String</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">"null"</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">setMessage</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">message</span> <span class="k">:</span> <span class="kt">String</span><span class="o">)</span><span class="k">:</span> <span class="kt">Unit</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">printMessage</span><span class="o">()</span> <span class="k">:</span> <span class="kt">Unit</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>μ‹¤μ  κµ¬ν„ ν΄λμ¤λ¥Ό μ¶”κ°€ν•΄λ³΄κ² μµλ‹λ‹¤.</p>

<div class="language-scala highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">TestImplements</span> <span class="k">extends</span> <span class="nc">Test</span> <span class="o">{</span>
    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">setMessage</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">contents</span><span class="k">:</span> <span class="kt">String</span><span class="o">)</span><span class="k">:</span> <span class="kt">Unit</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">{</span>
