</code></pre></div></div>

<p>λ‹¤μμΌλ΅ μ΄ μ‹¤μ²΄ ν΄λμ¤μ λ™μ‘μ„ μμ •ν•  μ μλ” νΈλ μ΄νΈλ¥Ό μƒμ„±ν•©λ‹λ‹¤.</p>

<div class="language-scala highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">trait</span> <span class="nc">TestTrait</span> <span class="k">extends</span> <span class="nc">Test</span> <span class="o">{</span>
